txt.en: 'So you wish to complete Volume III, Book 8? The story of pursuing the Fellowship across the plains of Rohan will be finished if you proceed.'\n\n'The choice is yours. If you wish to complete Volume III Book 8 of the Epic quest, speak to me once more.'
'Shall we continue? Finishing this quest will grant you completion of Volume III Book 8 of the Epic quest.'
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book 8 of the Epic quest series of Volume III.
